column5: After watching that specific part of the video a few times, I'm guessing perch not walleye.  After the camera pans back you can see the vertical stripes on it.  Way to spoil the party.  lol!  But you are correct.

Thanks all. I think it,s pretty cool  myself. Ya, I amuse myself. LOL   That was very neat.  How are you moving the camera around?  Thanks. Heres what I made a couple years back. Im going to be making a longer version when I get time.
